      "content": "IM内发起协商退数量    \n\n```Plain Text title=\"IM内房东发起的协商退订单数 代码\"\nSELECT\n    date(r.gmt_create),\n    count(DISTINCT order_id)\nFROM ba_phx.phx_base_phx_message_sync s\nJOIN ba_phx.phx_mdw_detail_trade_order_negotiate_refund r\n    ON s.to_user_id = r.phx_user_id\nWHERE \n    date(r.gmt_create) between '2025-12-15' and '2026-01-15'\n    AND get_json_object(msg_extension,'$.PHXExtensionType') = 'PHXExtensionTypeRefund'\nGROUP BY\n    date(r.gmt_create)\n```"
